Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:14.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.35,0:02:16.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be alone anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.35,0:02:16.11,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.35,0:02:19.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:21.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone who truly loves me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:26.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.07,0:02:27.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.43,0:02:30.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:46.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H575F66&\4c&H575F66&\pos(640,504)\blur3\1c&HCCD4DD&}Wolf and End of Shallowness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.59,0:02:55.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.68,0:03:00.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,he was just a small-minded trader.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:02.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:07.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If he can't do anything to comfort a lady as beautiful as you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.03,0:03:08.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,he's nothing but a failure as a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:13.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll protect me whatever happens, unlike him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:15.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:20.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if all my fortunes were taken away, I'd still have my love for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:23.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Craft Lawrence is nothing but a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.86,0:03:25.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Amarty...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:29.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.76,0:03:35.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, I warned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:39.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You were so full of confidence before, but look at you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:41.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This was unforeseen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:42.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Completely outside my expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.94,0:03:44.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:46.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:50.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:54.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what did you want to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.52,0:03:56.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're after a loan, I can't help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.91,0:03:58.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know which way the wind is blowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:01.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like setting sail and going out to sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.53,0:04:05.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,for an outsider like myself, the day to day market trends are unpredictable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.98,0:04:07.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.27,0:04:13.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't stop its value from rising any more than you can stop a raging horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:17.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The auction placards only increase in number the more they're sold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.74,0:04:20.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no signs that prices will be falling anytime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:24.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you're an omnipotent god, there's no way you can change that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.35,0:04:27.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll just have to play god.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:33.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt Amarty will allow himself to be caught by a predictable price drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:36.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning to crash the market?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:38.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my only choice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.83,0:04:41.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.29,0:04:46.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}I've got to turn all that pyrite he bought into plain rocks by sunset tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.67,0:04:56.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A ploy that Amarty wouldn't be able to read...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.88,0:04:59.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A ploy that will crash the market...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.60,0:05:01.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could such a trick exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:09.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at these!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:13.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're putting a lot on this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.92,0:05:16.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you leaving the wheat business for mining?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:19.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumor has it its value will double by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:20.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Double? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:22.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:28.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you close up shop for the festival, you'll miss a chance to set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:32.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be seriously buying wheat, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:43.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Lawrence!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:49.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:57.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote it just a moment ago at the request of your companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:01.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,200 silver in cash,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:08.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,300 silver worth of pyrite, and 200 silver in saleable property...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.81,0:07:11.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,These are Amarty's assets!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:20.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.72,0:07:25.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:26.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Amarty's handwriting?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.12,0:07:29.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That Horo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.62,0:07:31.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she make him sign another crazy contract? {split into two lines and reworded}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:55.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Take out all the cash I stored here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:57.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.03,0:08:09.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.01,0:08:10.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that guy, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.75,0:08:16.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:19.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch where you're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:22.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.03,0:08:23.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay... {added}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:31.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.98,0:08:37.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be so wary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.77,0:08:40.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just came to talk business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:44.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all the more reason to put up my guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:48.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Might you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:51.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:55.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You said business talk, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.58,0:09:12.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\3c&H000000&\fsp-2.5\3a&H55&\move(1680,600,-8678,600,0,61010)}Frequently as of late, television programs have been
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:20.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\3c&H000000&\fsp-2.5\3a&H55&\move(1825,600,-8558,600,0,61010)}illegally misappropriated for use on the internet. Distribution
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.72,0:09:42.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\3c&H000000&\fsp-2.5\3a&H55&\move(1735,600,-8621,600,0,61010)}of this program on the internet is crazy awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:42.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\3c&H000000&\fsp-1.5\fscx105\3a&H55&\move(1754,600,-8600,600,0,61010)}and we encourage you to keep at it. Remember to seed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:57.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.11,0:09:00.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:02.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get right to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.86,0:09:04.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to sell you some pyrite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:09.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to sell you some pyrite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.84,0:09:14.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,500 Trenni silver worth, at its current market value.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:17.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:18.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:24.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you're aware that I'm profiting off pyrite resale.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:27.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean to accomplish by selling it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:33.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could the rumors that you'd give up Horo as long as you get the money be true?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:39.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,By the name of St. Lambardos who watches over the Rowen Trading Guild from heaven,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:43.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear that I shall profess my sincere love to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.36,0:09:46.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's almost like a heroic knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.86,0:09:51.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But if that's the case, the only thing we can do is observe the opponent's actions directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:52.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How sneaky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:56.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.64,0:09:59.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:02.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I still care about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:05.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo is a very important person to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.65,0:10:07.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.39,0:10:10.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't intend to hand the pyrite over in a simple sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.01,0:10:12.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to sell on credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.43,0:10:16.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.16,0:10:22.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to sell you 500 Trenni silver worth of pyrite tomorrow evening at its current market price.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.69,0:10:27.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, why not discuss this tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.26,0:10:28.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:31.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to receive the payment now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:37.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I will accept 500 silver from you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:44.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And then tomorrow evening, I'll give you 500 silver worth of pyrite at its value right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:49.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So even if the value of pyrite rises tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:53.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll still receive 500 silver worth of pyrite at its current lower value.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.79,0:10:55.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.94,0:10:57.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,you catch on quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.25,0:11:03.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, if the value drops tomorrow, I'll also still receive the same amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.73,0:11:04.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:08.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How is this any different from a standard transaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:12.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you sell something and its value increases, you'd regret it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.76,0:11:14.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and if its value decreases, you'd be at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.89,0:11:17.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think of it that way, it's not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:20.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.42,0:11:22.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:27.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, even if you didn't have the money on hand, you could still acquire the goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:33.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And after that, no matter how much its value changed, you'd just have to pay back the original price.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:37.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So if its value rises, you'd make a profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.68,0:11:40.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's buying on credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:47.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So when I actually give you the pyrite, if its value has fallen then I'll have profited by that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.67,0:11:50.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many ways to conduct business, aren't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:53.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you get the idea now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:58.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand the meaning behind the deal you're proposing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:12:02.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I buy 500 silver worth of pyrite from you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:06.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,my profits will go up if its value increases,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:10.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but in the case that it goes down, it's possible I'll make an immeasurable loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.59,0:12:11.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, this is—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:12.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:17.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm challenging you to a duel, Amarty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.24,0:12:28.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even assuming the value of pyrite falls tomorrow evening,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:32.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd just have to sell some off beforehand, while the price is still high.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:40.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, I can step away from the duel whenever I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.71,0:12:47.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I can reach my goal with just a slight increase in value, this deal would be too unfair for you, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.42,0:12:53.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want to make a contract for the sake of my own profit, at your loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:55.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.84,0:12:58.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a disadvantage is just about right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.12,0:13:04.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There is the possibility that Horo rips up the contract that she signed with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:18.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you pay back the 1000 silver debt, you're relying dangerously on Horo accepting your proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:23.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My disadvantage is nothing compared to that risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.79,0:13:26.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard the two of you had quite a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:32.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In our travels, Horo has cried in my arms three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:36.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When she's like that, she's very cute,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:38.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but also quite stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:41.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She tends to say things she doesn't really mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:43.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.29,0:13:46.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:50.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:51.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me, {edited}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.54,0:13:58.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I had thought that taking everything from you would have been too harsh, which is why I initially declined.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.91,0:14:02.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you put it like that, I'll accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:07.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact I will strip you of all your poessessions!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:13.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we seal the contract then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.36,0:14:17.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:20.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.93,0:14:28.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is good beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.44,0:14:29.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you had any good ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.42,0:14:34.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't wheat sales pick up at the end of the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:35.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:38.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When that time comes, I'd like you to spread a rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:41.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to do anything risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:44.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be risky if you were to say it yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:47.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but there'd be no problem if it was the boy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.39,0:14:52.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to say this at a certain time and place:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:56.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"I guess it's about time for wheat prices to go up."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.62,0:15:07.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You plan to lower the price of these stones with a rumor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:08.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:16.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Most people buying pyrite are here to sell their wares, then pick up something else to take back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.75,0:15:20.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The most common load would be wheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:23.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When the time comes to buy, if they hear that the price of wheat is going up,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:29.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll sell off their pocket-money pyrite and rush off to buy what they originally came for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:33.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens, the value of pyrite will inevitably fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.90,0:15:38.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And when it reaches a critical point, it will plummet down to nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:44.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you were so simple-minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:48.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What if I said I plan to sell a substantial amount of pyrite at the same time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.79,0:15:50.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:53.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,One thousand Trenni silver worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:54.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A thousand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:54.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No wa— {edit}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.77,0:15:57.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea how much you'll lose by doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.55,0:15:59.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care how much its value drops.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.51,0:16:03.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you completely lost it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.12,0:16:04.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.17,0:16:07.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can get 500 silver worth of pyrite by the end of it all,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:11.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,however much the price rises or falls, I won't lose out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.75,0:16:15.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! You're selling on credit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:17.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:19.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So is that all you wanted me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:22.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there's one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:24.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to buy up Pyrite.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.27,0:16:29.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you make the contract after finding a buyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.04,0:16:32.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately I didn't have the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.78,0:16:34.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:38.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The best way to buy it up quietly, without affecting the market,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.21,0:16:44.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,would be to influence the town merchants to each buy a little, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:48.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind if you have to pay a little more than market value.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:51.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If they'll buy a relatively large amount, I'll pay in Rumione gold coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.60,0:16:55.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also pay you for your services.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:57.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Respectably, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:16:57.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.89,0:16:58.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.85,0:16:59.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:03.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'd pay you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:06.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And not any small amount, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:09.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you'll lose out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:11.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose out?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.69,0:17:13.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.24,0:17:16.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not asking you to make an investment, and of course I'll pay in cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:19.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What could you possibly have to lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:24.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be able to pay ten Rumione at best, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:27.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's more than enough for you to buy on proxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.87,0:17:33.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm asking you to travel a rocky mountain yourself and bring back a ridiculous amount or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:38.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're asking me to go around the market buying up pyrite, then it's the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:40.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What about that is the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:42.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no risks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:46.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just asking you to buy pyrite through your connections.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:50.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking at the risks from the perspective of a traveling merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.23,0:17:55.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a town merchant whose battlefield is this marketplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:18:02.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Town traders who look to profit from easy money have accepted that their primary business will suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:05.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the owner of this store,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.85,0:18:08.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but it isn't just my name that's at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:12.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The honor of myself, my wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:15.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and everyone related to us —
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:17.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,even my regular customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:19.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All of that is on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:29.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no virtue in a town merchant who shows no hesitation in jumping at every opportunity to make easy money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:36.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, making a little pocket money on the side isn't a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.27,0:18:41.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but buying up 500 silver worth of pyrite is a totally different story.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:44.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What would the townsfolk think of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.67,0:18:49.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In their eyes, I'd be nothing but a worthless merchant who threw his store to the curb on a gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.43,0:18:54.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you offer a reward that matches that risk?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.62,0:18:59.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even for a small shop like mine, the value of the name on the signboard is surprisingly high.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:04.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If that were tarnished, ten or twenty gold coins wouldn't be enough to buy it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.17,0:19:06.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:07.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:10.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm sorry for asking such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:16.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,With that companion of yours, I guess it's understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.91,0:19:23.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if you were to act a little less frantically, she wouldn't be swayed that easily, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.10,0:19:28.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after seeing her with you only once, that's the impression I get.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:30.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have some confidence in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:34.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A signed marriage certificate was handed to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.03,0:19:39.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If her guardian ratifies it, the marriage will be complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.22,0:19:47.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing had happened, of course I'd be confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:50.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"In this world, darkness lies an inch ahead," eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:56.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're still running the race because you have hope, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.45,0:19:57.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. {edited, orig: "Yeah." people didnt say "Yeah"  back then}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.95,0:20:00.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite a daredevil.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.03,0:20:01.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anyone else you can go to?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:06.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try asking Bartose for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:07.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:10.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get him to talk to that woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.26,0:20:11.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:14.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the chronicler.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.43,0:20:15.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:20.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman has control over this district.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:24.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You could say she's the means by which one communicates with the alchemists.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.57,0:20:30.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alchemists are easy targets for various reasons, but so many are able to gather here,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:33.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,mostly due to the presence of that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:35.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.48,0:20:39.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alchemists have pyrite, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:44.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to make trades without disrupting the market, you'll have to deal with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.58,0:20:45.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.87,0:20:51.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, their pyrite is untouched!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.12,0:20:52.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's about all I can do for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.99,0:20:57.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I refused to help, but I'm rooting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.86,0:20:59.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've learned something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.56,0:21:02.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That in itself is profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:06.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:09.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I can't do anything publicly,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.50,0:21:13.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,leaking out the amount of money someone's carrying wouldn't be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:14.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mark...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:16.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.69,0:21:19.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look into potential buyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:23.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the wind will blow your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.95,0:21:25.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.60,0:21:26.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.12,0:21:31.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:32.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:34.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so predictable it's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.07,0:21:39.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If she saw that face of yours, even that princess might do something bold. {Think he's trying to say this}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.96,0:21:42.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.33,0:23:52.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Wolf and Hope and Despair
